net.viktorc.pp4j.impl

    net.viktorc.pp4j.impl  
  • Classes in net.viktorc.pp4j.impl used by net.viktorc.pp4j.impl 
    Class and Description
    AbstractCommand
    An abstract implementation of the Command interface that stores all lines output to the process' standard out and standard error in response to the command.
    AbstractProcessManager
    An abstract implementation of the ProcessManager interface.
    ProcessPoolExecutor
    An implementation of the ProcessExecutorService interface for maintaining and managing a pool of pre-started processes.
    SimpleCommand
    A simple sub-class of the AbstractCommand abstract class that relies on lambda functions to implement the onOutput method and assumes that the command should always be executed and that the process generates an output in response to the command.
